{"tid":1666941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4點鐘黑社會記者會討論","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:04:11.000Z","uid":314636,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3a88d5bf66ae2dfb874edeb8acfa7ac73c903a","tid":1666941,"uid":314636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"今日謝蛇回歸了"},{"pid":"9cfaaf0fe80eb3687b659e559fe6386535420fc8","tid":1666941,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"849d1dc1a8e6c061118a55e5ab038db985b18e19","tid":1666941,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adc805dbbc6217e1e325791d87413cbc8cb075b","tid":1666941,"uid":118833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"謝Sir"},{"pid":"423cf226e5c3aad19b116ac7e224d4e4df4217dd","tid":1666941,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}